snippet.title: Pulang Insanity   Official Game Teaser 2019
snippet.description:
Coming Soon 2019 

Pulang : Insanity is a psychological horror games set in a mythical culture of Indonesia. planned to be released on the Steam platform in early 2019

#EnterInsanity #TheDevil_IsHere #PulangInsanity

Rudy, a man who once became poor and heavily indebted, he passed his poverty and became prosperous via the “Pesugihan” ritual, yet the happiness didn’t last long…
